2.0.name: wordpress/andrina-lite
2.0.description: Andrina is Elegant and beautiful Theme with Easy Customization Options built by InkThemes.com. The Andrina Theme features a uniquely curved designed feature section. Andrina Theme is perfect for all kinds of business and personal sites. You can easily convert the Theme into your own Niche. The Andrina Theme can tweaked easily using the Theme Options Panel like logos, intro texts and background. Andrina Theme supports five widgetized areas (two in the sidebar, Three in the footer).
